    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#78\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">absence</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>\"不在场的状态\"，14世纪末，源自古法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">absence</span> \"缺席\"（14世纪），源自拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">absentia</span>，抽象名词，源自 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">absentem</span>（主格 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">absens</span>）的现在分词，源自 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">abesse</span> \"离开，缺席\"，源自 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">ab</span> \"离开，远离\"（参见 <a href=\"/cn/word/ab-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of ab- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">ab-</a>）+ <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">esse</span> \"存在\"（源自 PIE 词根 <a href=\"/cn/word/*es-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *es- \" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">*es-</a> \"存在\"）。<span class=\"foreign notranslate\">Absence makes the heart grow fonder</span> 是英国诗人和作曲家托马斯·海恩斯·贝利（1797-1839）的歌曲\"美丽的岛屿\"中的一句歌词。</p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>"
    }
  ],
